Package: displayctl
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends},
 python3-click (>= 8.0),
 python3-rich (>= 10.0),
 x11-xserver-utils,
 udev
Recommends: wlr-randr, edid-decode, python3-pyinotify, libnotify-bin
Description: Multi-monitor display mode controller
 Control display modes (mirror, extend, second-only, PC-only)
 via CLI. Supports X11 (xrandr) and Wayland (wlr-randr) backends
 with automatic detection. Features profile save/load with EDID
 fingerprinting and hotplug daemon.
